data.description: Welcome to your charming 3 bedroom, 1 bath ranch home nestled on a quarter-acre lot. You'll step into the open concept living space with natural light streaming through the picturesque diamond shaped, lattice windows and large back sliding door. The seamless flow between the living room, kitchen, and dining areas creates an inviting atmosphere. Your updated kitchen with new energy star, stainless steel appliances, tiled back splash, and ample counter space make entertaining a dream. This home is the perfect blend of comfort, style and has plenty of backyard space in the fully fenced yard for summer barbecues, pets, and play-sets. Updates: brand new HVAC with a 10 year warranty, a renovated, encapsulated crawlspace with all new air ducts, an air conditioned shed with new flooring, storage space, and it’s equipped with electricity for the lights and TV. Centrally located near military bases, the interstate, shopping, CNU, and the neighborhood park and pool. Schedule your showing today!
